{"tid":1517951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"在囚人士被懲教人員毆打","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:44:32.000Z","uid":60545,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"895ca0e96ba46bc62bed4149e0da012766f7538d","tid":1517951,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"在囚人士被懲教人員毆打<br />\n2019/08/30 13:34<br />\n<br />\n一名荔枝角收押所的在囚人士指控被懲教人員毆打，他媽媽探望時發現及投訴。 <br />\n<br />\n受害人化名王先生現年四十多歲，他媽媽楊女士上月四日到收押所探望時，懲教人員指王先生身體不適，未能見面，楊女士隔天再去，見到兒子摸著心口，碎步走路，承認被打。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n楊女士投訴後，兒子才獲安排入院治療，留醫六日，並已報警。協助她的社區組織協會指，過往也收過在囚人士在赤柱監獄及荔枝角收押所被毆打的投訴，希望申訴專員介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/556030/即時新聞/在囚人士被懲教人員毆打\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F556030%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8sVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=27f9fc9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F556030%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93&h=52f13265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/556030/即時新聞/在囚人士被懲教人員毆打</a>"},{"pid":"c18b27e997b4152d5028de8dfd7070f8b9d4efc0","tid":1517951,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"0.3已入賬"},{"pid":"ba32189bf86d46131c39a00a65b7364a8558d8c6","tid":1517951,"uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c18b27e997b4152d5028de8dfd7070f8b9d4efc0","tid":1517951,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"0.3已入賬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"做乜嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm